#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn8.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn8.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.11:0.2"
msgid "1. Vaṅgīsavagga "
msgstr "1. With Vaṅgīsa "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn8.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Gaggarāsutta "
msgstr "11. At Gaggarā "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.421, sc1
msgctxt "sn8.11:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā campāyaṃ viharati gaggarāya pokkharaṇiyā tīre mahatā bhikkhusaṃghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi sattahi ca upāsakasatehi sattahi ca upāsikāsatehi anekehi ca devatāsahassehi. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Campā on the banks of the Gaggarā Lotus Pond, together with a large Saṅgha of around five hundred mendicants, seven hundred male and seven hundred female lay followers, and many thousands of deities. "

#. VAR: atirocati → ativirocati (mr)
msgctxt "sn8.11:1.2"
msgid "Tyāssudaṃ bhagavā atirocati vaṇṇena ceva yasasā ca. "
msgstr "But the Buddha outshone them all in beauty and glory. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.11:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato vaṅgīsassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Vaṅgīsa thought, "

msgctxt "sn8.11:1.4"
msgid "“ayaṃ kho bhagavā campāyaṃ viharati gaggarāya pokkharaṇiyā tīre mahatā bhikkhusaṃghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi sattahi ca upāsakasatehi sattahi ca upāsikāsatehi anekehi ca devatāsahassehi. "
msgstr "“The Buddha is staying near Campā on the banks of the Gaggarā Lotus Pond, together with a large Saṅgha of around five hundred mendicants, seven hundred male and seven hundred female lay followers, and many thousands of deities. "

msgctxt "sn8.11:1.5"
msgid "Tyāssudaṃ bhagavā atirocati vaṇṇena ceva yasasā ca. "
msgstr "And he outshines them all in beauty and glory. "

msgctxt "sn8.11:1.6"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ bhagavantaṃ sammukhā sāruppāya gāthāya abhitthaveyyan”ti. "
msgstr "Why don’t I extoll him in his presence with fitting verses?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn8.11:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso uṭṭhāyāsanā ekaṃsaṃ uttarāsaṅgaṃ karitvā yena bhagavā tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Vaṅgīsa got up from his seat, arranged his robe over one shoulder, raised his joined palms toward the Buddha, and said, "

msgctxt "sn8.11:2.2"
msgid "“paṭibhāti maṃ, bhagavā, paṭibhāti maṃ, sugatā”ti. "
msgstr "“I feel inspired to speak, Blessed One! I feel inspired to speak, Holy One!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.11:2.3"
msgid "“Paṭibhātu taṃ, vaṅgīsā”ti bhagavā avoca. "
msgstr "“Then speak as you feel inspired,” said the Buddha. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.11:2.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso bhagavantaṃ sammukhā sāruppāya gāthāya abhitthavi: "
msgstr "Then Vaṅgīsa extolled the Buddha in his presence with fitting verses: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.196, sc3
msgctxt "sn8.11:3.1"
msgid "“Cando yathā vigatavalāhake nabhe, "
msgstr "“Like the moon on a cloudless night, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.11:3.2"
msgid "Virocati vigatamalova bhāṇumā; "
msgstr "like the shining immaculate sun, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.11:3.3"
msgid "Evampi aṅgīrasa tvaṃ mahāmuni, "
msgstr "so too Aṅgīrasa, O great sage, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.11:3.4"
msgid "Atirocasi yasasā sabbalokan”ti. "
msgstr "your glory outshines the entire world.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
